This project includes the following components:

1. Core Orchestrator (aetherless-core)
   - Function lifecycle management
   - CRIU checkpoint/restore integration
   - Zero-copy shared memory IPC
   - Thread-safe function registry

2. Command-Line Interface (aetherless-cli)
   - CLI orchestrator commands
   - TUI dashboard
   - Configuration management

3. eBPF Data Plane (aetherless-ebpf)
   - XDP program loading and management
   - BPF map port-to-PID routing
   - Kernel-bypass networking

All components are solely authored by Ankit Pandey.
